data.title: Team GB Underwater Hockey
data.text:
This website is built using information sourced from multiple underwater hockey websites and Facebook pages. We strive to keep it up-to-date with the latest developments. Please note that this website is run by volunteers, so updates may not occur immediately. If you notice any missing information, issues, or have any suggestions, please don't hesitate to reach out to the developer.

Contact the developer Laura Moss: comms@gbuwh.co.uk
